<plot>"Not My Religion" is a fictional tale of a chance encounter between a Mermaid (Kelsey Matheson) and Jesus Christ (John Dickie). The entire piece takes place under water and is a comment on issues that affect most of the world, issues such as communication, relationships, the different view points and world of the two sexes, theology, innocence and loss.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?401109</url></doc>
